est-says-he-had-swastika-t-shirt-idea-for-over-eight-years-3838835">有“八年多”的T恤的想法</a>。它与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">一系列引起争议的帖子</a>一连串，使他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">对犹太社区进行了道歉，因为他过去的反犹太言论</a>，然后继续宣布自己为“纳粹”，并写道：“我爱希特勒”，并赞美亿万富翁和X老板<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）</a>是“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统就职典礼上对纳粹主义的指控</a>之后，“在Twitter上曾经是有史以来最有线的人”。</p><p>在星期三晚上（2月19日），这位有争议的说唱歌手似乎回避了他较早的评论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-after-reflection-3839623">X带着X分享“进一步反思”，他“意识到我不是纳粹”</a> 。</p><p>但是，现在，韦斯特（West）分享了更多的商品，其中包含swastika符号。在X上现在被删除的帖子中，他与标志分享了五个不同T恤的图像。他在昨晚的标题上（2月22日）在标题中写道：“产品酥脆。” </p><figure id="attachment_3840484" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840484" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840484" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter-400x300.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter-696x522.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-post-on-X-formally-Twitter-1392x1044.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye