ia-setlist-watch-footage-3595618">在八年来参加亿万富翁在印度举行的私人婚礼时，她的第一场完整表演</a>。</p><p>她的伴侣<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-found-not-guilty-in-hollywood-shooting-trial-3839212">A $ AP Rocky上周在他的2021年枪击事件中被判无罪</a>。洛杉矶陪审团因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-arrested-in-connection-with-shooting-in-2021-3208779">涉嫌向他的前朋友A $ ap Relli开枪</a>而被指控罪名成立。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-rejects-plea-deal-as-his-gun-trial-opens-in-los-angeles-3830874">面临24年的监禁</a>，并拒绝了一项认罪协议，监禁了180天。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-shares-statement-on-aap-rockys-gun-trial-verdict-3839304">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）对无罪释放的回应说</a>：“荣耀属于上帝和上帝！感谢他的怜悯！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f64f-1f3ff.png" alt="🙏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />透明</p><p>蕾哈娜（Rihanna）帖子在新<a href="https://www.nme.com">专辑</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-gives-update-on-new-album-its-not-going-to-be-anything-that-anybody-expects-3840453">上提供了更新：“它不会成为任何人期望的任何东西”</a> 。</p> ;
